.\" $Id$
.TH GPTLreset 3 "January, 2009" "GPTL"

.SH NAME
GPTLreset \- Reset all timer contents to zero. 

.SH SYNOPSIS
.B C Interface:
.nf
int GPTLreset (void);
.fi

.B Fortran Interface:
.nf
integer gptlreset ()
.fi

.SH DESCRIPTION
Reset all timer contents to zero.  This includes any embedded PAPI counters.

.SH RESTRICTIONS
.B GPTLinitialize()
must have been called. This function must be called by the master thread only.

.SH RETURN VALUES
On success, this function returns 0.
On error, a negative error code is returned and a descriptive message
printed. 

.SH EXAMPLES
.nf         
.if t .ft CW

if (GPTLreset () != 0)
  handle_error (1);

.if t .ft P
.fi
